VALUES ('288dd033-2c4d-4125-9d1e-9e44358a2d9e', '270', NULL, 'i - s imposed at any other criminal provision, except', 'penal_code', 'en', '.- Offense to a Minister of Worship Is punishable by imprisonment of one (01) months to three (03) years, the one who strike or publicly insult the minister of worship during the exercise of his ministry. 98');
