VALUES ('b47e1a79-fb30-4f02-b732-5e0b95f343c6', '344', NULL, 'i - s imposed at any other criminal provision, except', 'penal_code', 'en', '.- Youth corruption (1) is punished with imprisonment of one (01) to CING (05) years and a fine of twenty thousand (20,000) to one million (1,000,000) francs, the one who excites, promotes or facilitates the debauchery or corruption of a minor twenty -one (21) years. (2) The sorrows are doubled if the victim is less than sixteen (16) years. (4) The jurisdiction may also pronounce the forfeiture of article 30 of the this code and deprive the convicted person during the same period of the authority Parental, of all guardianship or curatorship.');
